    <item>
      <title>铜价因中国潜在刺激措施和需求增长而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/copper-rises-amid-potential-chinese-stimulus-demand-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者预期中国可能出台刺激措施，且各国央行开始放松政策周期，铜价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/copper-rises-amid-potential-chinese-stimulus-demand-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 16:32:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗森伯格称招聘率已引起美联储关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-23/hiring-rate-has-caught-the-fed-s-eye-rosenberg-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗森伯格研究公司的戴维·罗森伯格谈到降息对美国经济的影响。他表示，政策制定者需要密切关注招聘率。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
