      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 11:01:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>降息引发新兴市场债券 ETF 热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/emerging-market-etfs-rebound-from-losses-rise-560-7-mln</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美联储宽松周期的乐观情绪激发了风险偏好，投资者上周将资金投入购买新兴市场债券的交易所交易基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/emerging-market-etfs-rebound-from-losses-rise-560-7-mln</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 10:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗表示准备缓解以色列紧张局势后油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于燃料需求前景疲软，以及伊朗和以色列之间的冲突在最近爆发后有可能缓和，油价下跌。]]></description>
